                    </p>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 thing" style="text-align: center; margin: auto;">
    <h1>MOST POPULAR POSTS</h1>
    <a href="~/Posts/0"><img class="tint" src="~/content/1.jpg" style="width: 10em; height: 10em;" /></a>
    <a href="~/Posts/1"><img class="tint" src="~/content/2.png" style="width: 10em; height: 10em;" /></a>
    <a href="~/Posts/2"><img class="tint" src="~/content/4.jpg" style="width: 10em; height: 10em;" /></a>
    <a href="~/Posts/3"><img class="tint" src="~/content/3.jpg" style="width: 10em; height: 10em;" /></a>
</div>

<hr>
